6ae15bcaa9d190baa8b45c31adf50795","tid":201471,"uid":34716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:12:48.000Z","msg":"好黑暗架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個次去到呢 上界啲人個個一人兩票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為其他層代表唔去個個選會呢 <br />\n就會問佢地授權比上界啲人幫佢地投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上都係上界啲人做返"},{"pid":"a8204fd7c9de1dc867066db05e8c8524c0a2903d","tid":201471,"uid":29925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:29:15.000Z","msg":"其實建制派嘅c9做到嘅機會大啲<br />\n<br />\n巴打你最好留意下同一棟樓有冇啲同你同立場嘅人 傾好咗先一齊搶做層代表<br />\n如果唔係就好難同啲c9鬥<br />\n<br />\n如果最後真係選唔到 咁都可以諗下做核數"},{"pid":"d202f0d092a89f4f36f1ca2a98ee67ad816c1e74","tid":201471,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92bf60febfcd8d8df0517a481b16dfb76add2cd5","tid":201471,"uid":34033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:34:19.000Z","msg":"可以玩下<br />\n但入到去預孤立無援<br />\n因為區議員，無論紅唔紅底都會安排樁腳c9去選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過其實當識人都唔錯<br />\n選中啲人、食蕉都忌你三分"},{"pid":"64440b37a21e0c3ed02b525a96573171bd39274f","tid":201471,"uid":48266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:34:38.000Z","msg":"互助委員會無咩用 <br />\n係搞下旅行果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你要做層代表先 到大選個日先會選主席秘書司庫<br />\n基本上係區議會黎講 你冇咩權力<br />\n又冇錢收 全部野都係義務"},{"pid":"31d209122571a4f5aa83bd9f10048b696419c597","tid":201471,"uid":34033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:35:26.000Z","msg":"workload方面你放心<br />\n啲廢中c9字都唔識隻<br />\n邊有心機同你成日開會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6716d2b62ebf99355363bd9cff3d411ceb85ef6f","tid":201471,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:38:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好黑暗架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個次去到呢 上界啲人個個一人兩票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為其他層代表唔去個個選會呢 <br />\n就會問佢地授權比上界啲人幫佢地投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上都係上界啲人做返</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b52cdf9d825be226803531827c7c0595890df51","tid":201471,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實建制派嘅c9做到嘅機會大啲<br />\n<br />\n巴打你最好留意下同一棟樓有冇啲同你同立場嘅人 傾好咗先一齊搶做層代表<br />\n如果唔係就好難同啲c9鬥<br />\n<br />\n如果最後真係選唔到 咁都可以諗下做核數</blockquote><br />\n好，唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21964320446962af44295df13a01e23efdf8594","tid":201471,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:05:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好黑暗架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個次去到呢 上界啲人個個一人兩票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為其他層代表唔去個個選會呢 <br />\n就會問佢地授權比上界啲人幫佢地投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上都係上界啲人做返</blockquote><br />\n今年係第一屆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9034e8e90cb297a2347ec74080df5b84ec04f6e9","tid":201471,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好黑暗架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個次去到呢 上界啲人個個一人兩票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 